snippet.textDisplay:
I listened to a few lines that were edited on a video of flood affected areas here in Pakistan and I fell in love with the lyrics, music and the gem of voices. Glad I found this gem. 
Sanu soda nai pugda 
Ravi tu channa puchda 
Ki haal ay Sutlej da ...... 
Love from the other half of Punjab , from a small town of Jalalpur Pir wala where Ravi , chenab and Sutlej all three river meets. But it seems they are not happy this time. ❤️‍🩹❤
